# Explore Wrapprs

The Explore tab (opens new window) allows you to review public Wrapprs.

After paying a minting fee, you can send a Wrappr NFT to your chosen account, such as a DAO or multisig.

These NFTs will be viewable on other NFT gallery sites such as OpenSea (opens new window) and LooksRare (opens new window), as well as your wallet, such as Rainbow (opens new window).
